	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">吸引了Rihanna和Beyoncé的郭培，其实背后很有故事</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-05-20 06:55:51 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-message">10</span>
				<span class="iconfont icon-heart">35</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</a>

                    </div>
                    <div class="packery-item article">
                        <!-- 普通文章格子，占位1x1，智能占位 -->
<!-- 传入参数：article -->

<a href="/articles/27143.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/27143/indexMediumPc2/27143.jpg?1463739354" alt="失踪的埃及航空804航班，失联前都经历了什么？">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/5/medium/5.png?1411569637" alt="城市">
			<span>城市</span>
		</p>
